name: Trapped tripping in the trash twins' tailgaiting trailer toilet
description: The background is painted with metallic paint so it gets super trippy when it catches the light! I giggled the entire time painting this. My first time painting a detailed face! If you don't know who this is or what it's from, stop what you're doing right now and go binge all 14 seasons of It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia. It's totally worth it.
